    <string name="quick_guide">
    <![CDATA[
        <b>📖 Quick Guide :</b><br><br>
        1) From the main menu, choose <b>Encrypt Image</b> or <b>Decrypt Image</b>.<br>
        2) For <b>Encryption</b>: upload an image → press <b>Encrypt</b> → a secret key is generated.<br>
        3) You can Copy, download, or share the encrypted image with the secret key.<br>
        4) For <b>Decryption</b>: upload the encrypted image and enter the same secret key.<br>
        5) If biometric is enabled in settings, authentication is required for decryption.<br>
        6) The decrypted image is shown with a <b>30-second viewing limit</b>.<br>
        7) You can also save decrypted image into the <b>Private Folder</b>.
    ]]>
</string>
    <string name="quick_guide_text">
    <![CDATA[
        <b>📖 Quick Guide :</b><br><br>
        1) From Main Menu choose <b>Encrypt</b> or <b>Decrypt</b>.<br>
        2) For <b>Encryption</b> → Enter your <b>text</b> and a <b>password</b>.<br>
        3) Tap <b>Encrypt</b> to get cipher text.<br>
        4) For <b>Decryption</b> → Paste cipher + password.<br>
        5) If biometric is enabled in settings, authentication is required for decryption.<br>
        6) You can also save decrypted text into the <b>Private Folder</b>.<br>
        ⚠ Wrong password Leads to decryption fail.<br>
    ]]>
</string>
    <string name="quick_guide_file">
    <![CDATA[
        <b>📖 Quick Guide :</b><br><br>
        1) From Main Menu choose <b>Encrypt File</b> or <b>Decrypt File</b>.<br>
        2) For <b>Encryption</b> : Upload file → enter password → <b>Encrypt</b>.<br>
        3) You can Copy/Save/Share encrypted file.<br>
        4) For <b>Decryption</b> : Upload encrypted file → enter password → <b>Decrypt</b>.<br>
        5) ⚠ Wrong password leads to decryption fail.<br>
        6) If biometric is enabled in settings, authentication is required for decryption.<br>
        7) You can also save decrypted files into the <b>Private Folder</b>.
    ]]>
</string>
